#| "line with the only character \"#\", followed by a list of edges (one edge "
#| "per line)."
msgid ""
"The file starts with a list of nodes (one node per line), followed by a line "
"with the only character <quote>#</quote>, followed by a list of edges (one "
"edge per line)."
msgstr ""
"FAil algab tippude loendiga (üks tipp rea kohta), millele järgneb rida, "
"millel on ainult märk \"#\". Sellele järgneb seoste loend (üks seos igal "
"real)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A node consists of an integer (identifier), followed by a space, followed by "
"an arbitrary string."
msgstr ""
"Tipp koosneb täisarvust (identifikaator), millele järgneb tühik, millele "
"järgneb suvaline string."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An edge consists of two integers (identifiers) separated by a space, "
"followed by a space, followed by an arbitrary string. It is assumed that the "
"directed edge points from the first identifier to the second identifier."
msgstr ""
"Seos koosneb kahest tühikuga eraldatud täisarvust (identifikaatoritest), "
"millele järgneb tühik, millele järgneb suvaline string. Eeldatakse, et "
"suunaga seos kulgeb esimeselt identifikaatorilt teisele."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:351 index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Näide"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"1 starting node\n"
"2 transmitter\n"
"3 sink\n"
"#\n"
